  "detailed_description": "<h1>Coming soon - Grunn!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Pilfer is a stealth game in which the player is free to explore a small town filled with NPCs that live their own life. Sneak into their houses, steal their silverware, and make it to the online leaderboard!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206260/extras/fb65fc8db904fa6da6367adc3806caf0.poster.avif?t=1726498167\" width=560 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206260/extras/fb65fc8db904fa6da6367adc3806caf0.webm?t=1726498167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206260/extras/fb65fc8db904fa6da6367adc3806caf0.mp4?t=1726498167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 10-20 minutes of playtime.<br></li><li> A small town to explore.<br></li><li> Various NPCs with their own schedule.<br></li><li> Special items like swords and gems to find.<br></li><li> A lock-picking minigame.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206260/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1726498167\" width=200 height=70 /></span><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ",
